TITLE: Creating subscriptions with new API signatures in ROS2
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to create subscriptions in ROS2 with updated signatures that include rclcpp::QoS and option classes, replacing deprecated methods. It requires including the rclcpp library, and the callback function must match the message type. It ensures users follow the newer, more flexible API for subscriptions.
