TITLE: Using push_ros_namespace for Namespace Management in ROS 2 Launch Files
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to handle namespaces in ROS 2 launch files using push_ros_namespace within a group tag, including absolute namespaces and node namespace specification.
