DESCRIPTION: Sets the `transform` field of the `TransformStamped` message. The translation (x, y, z) components are directly assigned from command-line arguments. The rotation is calculated by converting Euler angles (roll, pitch, yaw from arguments) into a quaternion using the `quaternion_from_euler` helper function, and then assigned to the rotation (x, y, z, w) components.
